Detailed Description

cvmx_l2c_grpwrr0

L2C_GRPWRR0 = L2C PP Weighted Round #0 Register

Description: Defines Weighted rounds(32) for Group PLC0,PLC1

Notes:

  • Starvation of a group 'could' occur, unless SW takes the precaution to ensure that each GROUP participates in at least 1(of 32) rounds (ie: At least 1 bit(of 32) should be clear).
